263
00:15:51,160 --> 00:15:53,080
{\an8}[exciting music plays]

264
00:16:00,460 --> 00:16:03,100
[commentator 1] <i>Racing, then,
towards the first corner!</i>

265
00:16:03,140 --> 00:16:04,920
{\an8}[exciting music continues]

266
00:16:07,300 --> 00:16:08,740
{\an8}[commentator 1] <i>And there's contact!</i>

267
00:16:16,000 --> 00:16:16,940
Fuck!

268
00:16:16,980 --> 00:16:18,780
-He's fucked it up.
-That's it.

269
00:16:24,020 --> 00:16:26,340
{\an8}[Ocon] Fuck's sake.
I got massively hit, guys.

270
00:16:30,960 --> 00:16:32,240
{\an8}[Gasly] I don't understand.

271
00:16:37,040 --> 00:16:38,200
[Loos] <i>Too much damage.</i>

272
00:16:42,480 --> 00:16:45,960
{\an8}[Peckett] <i>Esteban, this is gonna be
terminal, please. We're retiring.</i>

273
00:16:46,940 --> 00:16:51,420
[commentator 3] <i>And that's a second double
"did not finish" in a row for Alpine.</i>

274
00:16:51,460 --> 00:16:52,920
<i>Disaster for Otmar.</i>

275
00:17:01,840 --> 00:17:05,580
[Szafnauer] Every weekend, things happen,
