00:20:26,120 --> 00:20:27,220
[Brown] Never a dull moment.

326
00:20:27,260 --> 00:20:28,720
-[man] I know.
-[Brown] Crazy.

327
00:20:29,240 --> 00:20:31,060
-[man] What a fucking...
-[Brown chuckles]

