00:23:40,240 --> 00:23:43,920
That's a really difficult gig to take on.

394
00:23:45,380 --> 00:23:48,480
And that team is gonna be
on its knees right now.

395
00:23:50,320 --> 00:23:51,760
One of Bruno's first focuses

